{"h987095b6g9160g450fg981fgcee2da9378b3": ["Treefather watch over you.", "322cf8d2-32ee-453f-987e-f12b32652b5d", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_ShadowDruid_AD_OpposedPacified.html", "9a8d67e3-faa3-f30b-dce4-6679f5ceaff4"], "hdcf4ced2gdec6g4fecga67cg83bbc5733d8c": ["Halsin will find us in ruin. We have lost so much.", "322cf8d2-32ee-453f-987e-f12b32652b5d", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_ShadowDruid_AD_OpposedPacified.html", "5e72937a-a4ba-3577-d3a2-a79d61d9cbfe"], "h6c66aee2g53efg4677ga657g79ab611dcdcf": ["If only you had said something, Kagha. I would have helped you.", "322cf8d2-32ee-453f-987e-f12b32652b5d", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_ShadowDruid_AD_OpposedPacified.html", "89945a49-6731-f969-0b1d-065cacd2cb2d"], "h38ce7b47g4c27g428dg8f8dg5a3d320f84e6": ["So much death. So little justice.", "322cf8d2-32ee-453f-987e-f12b32652b5d", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_ShadowDruid_AD_OpposedPacified.html", "159abdd4-a82d-42ae-dfdd-6ad9a0bbfc41"], "h007a3f66gcfeeg461fgb280g54488c3f8bde": ["May Silvanus' grace teach you in death what you did not learn in life, Kagha.", "322cf8d2-32ee-453f-987e-f12b32652b5d", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_ShadowDruid_AD_OpposedPacified.html", "94fcab3b-9a54-3172-14c0-c3338bb1cb8a"], "h1d772ddagb315g497bga973g37d3b93efd3c": ["How could I have been so blind?", "322cf8d2-32ee-453f-987e-f12b32652b5d", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_ShadowDruid_AD_OpposedPacified.html", "3379b2f7-cb27-6cf0-239d-2b7a0ae0ec1a"], "hc3685d47g15e1g443fg8820g52c3a602629a": ["Halsin would have stopped this.", "322cf8d2-32ee-453f-987e-f12b32652b5d", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_ShadowDruid_AD_OpposedPacified.html", "cb216541-b7d0-d65e-b2d6-c747e5c7de21"], "h89e99cfdgb8bfg47dbg99e8g4aab225627af": ["I should have seen the signs. She had gone too far.", "322cf8d2-32ee-453f-987e-f12b32652b5d", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_ShadowDruid_AD_OpposedPacified.html", "3573d3a1-7f99-2376-2195-154d5e79a817"], "hcbd37be9ge368g4a47g8508g7666fd75654a": ["Such is betrayal: a poison